    <br>
    <h2>Privacy Policies</h2>
    <p> You may consult this list to find the Privacy Policy for each of the advertising partners of Tolga Özkaya's Portfolio Website.</p>
    <p>Third-party ad servers or ad networks uses technologies like cookies, JavaScript, or Web Beacons that are used in their respective advertisements and links that appear on Tolga Özkaya's Portfolio Website, which are sent directly to users' browser. They automatically receive your IP address when this occurs. These technologies are used to measure the effectiveness of their advertising campaigns and/or to personalize the advertising content that you see on websites that you visit.</p>
    <p>Note that Tolga Özkaya's Portfolio Website has no access to or control over these cookies that are used by third-party advertisers.</p>
    <br>
    <h2>Third Party Privacy Policies</h2>
